  }, "Learn to read quickly and techniques to improve memory"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Find a mentor (for software development / personal growth)")), mdx("p", null, "Short-term goals:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Read at least one high-quality book per month about business and marketing"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "By the end of 2020, have at least 500 subscribers on the Medium platform"), mdx("li", {
